  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This phase II randomised, double blind, placebo controlled, multicentre trial is designed to
      assess the efficacy and safety of continuous icotinib plus chemotherapy versus chemotherapy
      alone in patients who have progressed after benefiting from previous second or third-line
      icotinib treatment (more than 6 months) in locally advanced or metastatic non-small cell lung
      cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
